                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000528-80-defend832 t18000528-80-punish463"></join>
               fined 1s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Baron CHAMBRE.</p>
